{"surah":{"number":91,"name":"الشمس","englishName":"Ash-Shams","englishTranslation":"The Sun","ayahCount":15},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:48.676Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"By the sun and its brightness","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلشَّمْسِ","english":"By the sun","translit":"wal-shamsi","root":"شمس"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَضُحَىٰهَا","english":"and its brightness","translit":"waḍuḥāhā","root":"ضحو"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And [by] the moon when it follows it","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْقَمَرِ","english":"And the moon","translit":"wal-qamari","root":"قمر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"when","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَلَىٰهَا","english":"it follows it","translit":"talāhā","root":"تلو"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And [by] the day when it displays it","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ","english":"And the day","translit":"wal-nahāri","root":"نهر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"when","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"جَلَّىٰهَا","english":"it displays it","translit":"jallāhā","root":"جلو"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And [by] the night when it covers it","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّيْلِ","english":"And the night","translit":"wa-al-layli","root":"ليل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"when","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَغْشَىٰهَا","english":"it covers it","translit":"yaghshāhā","root":"غشو"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"And [by] the sky and He who constructed it","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"And the heaven","translit":"wal-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and (He) Who","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بَنَىٰهَا","english":"constructed it","translit":"banāhā","root":"بني"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"And [by] the earth and He who spread it","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"And the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and by (He) Who","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"طَحَىٰهَا","english":"spread it","translit":"ṭaḥāhā","root":"طحو"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"And [by] the soul and He who proportioned it","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَنَفْسٍۢ","english":"And (the) soul","translit":"wanafsin","root":"نفس"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and (He) Who","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"سَوَّىٰهَا","english":"proportioned it","translit":"sawwāhā","root":"سوي"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"And inspired it [with discernment of] its wickedness and its righteousness,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَلْهَمَهَا","english":"And He inspired it","translit":"fa-alhamahā","root":"لهم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فُجُورَهَا","english":"(to distinguish) its wickedness","translit":"fujūrahā","root":"فجر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَتَقْوَىٰهَا","english":"and its righteousness","translit":"wataqwāhā","root":"وقي"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"He has succeeded who purifies it,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"Indeed","translit":"qad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَفْلَحَ","english":"he succeeds","translit":"aflaḥa","root":"فلح"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَن","english":"who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"زَكَّىٰهَا","english":"purifies it","translit":"zakkāhā","root":"زكو"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And he has failed who instills it [with corruption].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","english":"And indeed","translit":"waqad","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَابَ","english":"he fails","translit":"khāba","root":"خيب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَن","english":"who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"دَسَّىٰهَا","english":"buries it","translit":"dassāhā","root":"دسو"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Thamud denied [their prophet] by reason of their transgression,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَّبَتْ","english":"Denied","translit":"kadhabat","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ثَمُودُ","english":"Thamud","translit":"thamūdu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِطَغْوَىٰهَآ","english":"by their transgression","translit":"biṭaghwāhā","root":"طغي"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"When the most wretched of them was sent forth.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذِ","english":"When","translit":"idhi","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱنۢبَعَثَ","english":"(was) sent forth","translit":"inbaʿatha","root":"بعث"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَشْقَىٰهَا","english":"(the) most wicked of them","translit":"ashqāhā","root":"شقو"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"And the messenger of Allah [Salih] said to them, \"[Do not harm] the she-camel of Allah or [prevent her from] her drink.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَالَ","english":"But said","translit":"faqāla","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"to them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَسُولُ","english":"(the) Messenger","translit":"rasūlu","root":"رسل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَاقَةَ","english":"(It is the) she-camel","translit":"nāqata","root":"نوق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَسُقْيَـٰهَا","english":"and her drink","translit":"wasuq'yāhā","root":"سقي"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"But they denied him and hamstrung her. So their Lord brought down upon them destruction for their sin and made it equal [upon all of them].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ","english":"But they denied him","translit":"fakadhabūhu","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَعَقَرُوهَا","english":"and they hamstrung her","translit":"faʿaqarūhā","root":"عقر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَدَمْدَمَ","english":"So destroyed","translit":"fadamdama","root":"دمدم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَبُّهُم","english":"their Lord","translit":"rabbuhum","root":"ربب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِذَنۢبِهِمْ","english":"for their sin","translit":"bidhanbihim","root":"ذنب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَسَوَّىٰهَا","english":"and leveled them","translit":"fasawwāhā","root":"سوي"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"And He does not fear the consequence thereof.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَخَافُ","english":"He fears","translit":"yakhāfu","root":"خوف"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عُقْبَـٰهَا","english":"its consequences","translit":"ʿuq'bāhā","root":"عقب"}]}]}
